Package com.idevicesinc.sweetblue.internal.android

Class P_DeviceHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.idevicesinc.sweetblue.internal.android.P_DeviceHolder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UsesCustomNull
    public final class P_DeviceHolder
extends java.lang.Object
implements UsesCustomNull
    Class used to temporarily hold an instance of BluetoothDevice. This is only meant to wrap callbacks from the native layer to the internal layer. Once in the native layer, the device will be passed into an instance of IBluetoothDevice.
